Package: mongolite
Type: Package
Title: Streaming Mongo I/O Client
Description: Implements R bindings to the high-performance MongoDB C driver and
    high-level tools in the same spirit as jsonlite.
Version: 0.1
Date: 2015-03-27
Author: Jeroen Ooms
Maintainer: Jeroen Ooms <jeroen.ooms@stat.ucla.edu>
Depends: methods
Imports: jsonlite
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/jeroenooms/mongolite
BugReports: https://github.com/jeroenooms/mongolite/issues
SystemRequirements:
    OpenSSL: libssl-dev (deb) or openssl-devel (rpm),
    SASL: libsasl2-dev (deb) or cyrus-sasl-devel (rpm)
